text: The Marine 2 is a 2009 American action movie directed by Roel Reiné, written by Christopher Borrelli and John Chapin Morgan, and produced by Michael Lake. The movie stars are Ted DiBiase Jr., Temuera Morrison, Lara Cox, Robert Coleby and Michael Rooker. It is the stand-alone sequel to The Marine, starring John Cena, and it is the second in the movie series. This was Ted DiBiase's film debut. The movie was released on DVD and Blu-ray in the United States on December 29, 2009. ==References== ==Other websites== * * Category:2009 action movies Category:2009 thriller movies Category:American action thriller movies Category:English-language movies Category:20th Century Fox movies Category:Movies set in South Carolina Category:Movies about the United States Marine Corps Category:Movies directed by Roel Reiné
